response.overview: Alaska Video Postcards presents "Alaska's Wild Denali." This is an hour long film about the wildlife and wonders of Denali National Park.  Produced, filmed and edited by Todd Hardesty.  Narration by Peter Thomas.  See grizzlies, caribou, wolves and many more animals that live in the forests and tundra of Denali National Park.
response.title: Alaska's Wild Denali
